urlText: L2 Randwick Line and L3 Kingsford Line weeknight full closures due to maintenance
content:
From Monday 11 to Wednesday 13 December, nightly from 9pm to 1am, L2 Randwick Line and L3 Kingsford Line light rail services will not run due to planned trackwork and maintenance works.
 
During this time, use alternative transport including: 
  • Replacement bus services or regular bus services between Central Chalmers Street and Randwick or Juniors Kingsford,
  • Train services, regular bus services or walk, between Circular Quay and Central Chalmers Street.
See the news story for more information. Allow extra travel time and use the Trip Planner to see if your travel is affected.
